### Login as Super Admin
POST {{api}}/user/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "12345678"
}

###

### Create Admin
POST {{api}}/admin/admins
Authorization: Bearer 
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Library Admin",
  "email": "library-admin@example.com",
  "password": "12345678",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### List Admins
GET {{api}}/admin/admins
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

