### Create Subscription
POST {{api}}/admin/subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriptionAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 177,
  "courseId": "course-members"
}

###

### List Subscriptions
GET {{api}}/admin/subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriptionAdminToken}}

###

### Get Subscription
GET {{api}}/admin/subscription/29
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriptionAdminToken}}

###

### Update Subscription
PUT {{api}}/admin/subscription/29
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriptionAdminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "endsAt": "2027-01-01T00:00:00.000Z"
}

###

### Delete Subscription
DELETE {{api}}/admin/subscription/29
Authorization: Bearer {{subscriptionAdminToken}}

###



