###

### Course List
GET {{api}}/course

###

### Get Public Course
GET {{api}}/course/course-public

###

### Get Members Course
GET {{api}}/course/course-members

###

### My Communications
GET {{api}}/communication/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Get Communication #1
GET {{api}}/communication/199
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Create Communication
POST {{api}}/communication
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "referenceId": "public-page",
  "type": "query",
  "message": "This is a test communication."
}

